<section class="section-block">
	<h2>PBX features</h2>
	<ul class="features-grid">
		<li class="feature">
			<h3>Extensions and users</h3>
			<p>Manage users, extensions, caller ID, and device credentials from the VoiceTel account workflow.</p>
		</li>
		<li class="feature">
			<h3>Voicemail</h3>
			<p>Provide business voicemail workflows with routing and notification behavior defined during onboarding.</p>
		</li>
		<li class="feature">
			<h3>Ring groups</h3>
			<p>Route calls to teams, departments, or on-call groups without custom application code.</p>
		</li>
		<li class="feature">
			<h3>Business hours</h3>
			<p>Use schedules to route calls differently during open, closed, holiday, and emergency modes.</p>
		</li>
		<li class="feature">
			<h3>Attendant menus</h3>
			<p>Build simple IVR front doors for sales, support, billing, and after-hours routing.</p>
		</li>
		<li class="feature">
			<h3>VoiceTel Phone</h3>
			<p>Pair hosted users with web, desktop, and mobile calling where enabled.</p>
		</li>
