<section class="section-block faq-block">
	<h2>PBX FAQ</h2>
	<details class="faq-item">
		<summary>Can we keep existing desk phones?</summary>
		<p>Position this as an onboarding question. Device compatibility depends on SIP support, firmware, provisioning, and security policy.</p>
	</details>
	<details class="faq-item">
		<summary>Can hosted PBX use VoiceTel numbers?</summary>
		<p>Yes, numbers and emergency-service records is managed through the VoiceTel number workflow.</p>
	</details>
</section>
